Hey, I got my hands on some Jaguar motor controllers (the newer black ones, MDL-BDC24) and I’m using them for a robotics project. I want to include the model of the motor controller in my CAD document, but Ive SCOURED the internet and I cant find a single source that still exists where the CAD can be retreived. Luminary Micro’s website is dead, seems like TI never released a CAD model, and every database that I can find on ancient CD threads seems dead. If anyone has the model and can help me out, it would be greatly appreciated
